# =============================================================================
# Financial Modeling Prep API Key (Optional but Recommended)
# =============================================================================
#
# Get your FREE API key at: https://site.financialmodelingprep.com/developer/docs
# 
# Free tier includes:
#   - 250 API calls/day (sufficient for analyzing multiple stocks)
#   - 5 years of annual EPS data (converted to ~20 quarterly estimates)
#
# Without this key:
#   - Charts will only show ~1 year of history (Yahoo Finance limitation)
#
# With this key:
#   - Charts will show ~5 years of history
#   - More accurate P/E band statistics from longer price history
#
# To use:
#   1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
#   2. Replace 'your_api_key_here' with your actual API key
#   3. Run the analyzer: python3 pe_band_analyzer.py
#
# Alternatively, set the environment variable directly:
#   export FMP_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
#
# =============================================================================

FMP_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
